# Edge Cases & Debugging
# Demonstrates error responses, slow requests (spinner test), and various status codes.

### 200 OK
GET https://httpbin.org/status/200

### 201 Created
POST https://httpbin.org/status/201

### 204 No Content
DELETE https://httpbin.org/status/204

### 301 Redirect (followed automatically)
GET https://httpbin.org/redirect/1

### 400 Bad Request
GET https://httpbin.org/status/400

### 401 Unauthorized
GET https://httpbin.org/status/401

### 403 Forbidden
GET https://httpbin.org/status/403

### 404 Not Found
GET https://httpbin.org/status/404

### 500 Internal Server Error
GET https://httpbin.org/status/500

### 503 Service Unavailable
GET https://httpbin.org/status/503

## ── Slow responses (test the spinner) ───────────────────────
## These intentionally delay — watch the animated spinner and elapsed time counter.

### 3-second delay
GET https://httpbin.org/delay/3
Accept: application/json

### 7-second delay
GET https://httpbin.org/delay/7
Accept: application/json

### 10-second delay (stress test)
GET https://httpbin.org/delay/10
Accept: application/json

### ── Response formats ────────────────────────────────────────

### JSON response (auto-colorized)
GET https://httpbin.org/json

### HTML response
GET https://httpbin.org/html

### XML response
GET https://httpbin.org/xml

### UTF-8 encoded response
GET https://httpbin.org/encoding/utf8

### Gzip-compressed response
GET https://httpbin.org/gzip

### Large response (tests output handling)
GET https://httpbin.org/bytes/4096
